周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-recalls-nearly-falling-off-a-cliff-while-filming-new-music-video-3602486">马斯格雷夫斯透露，她在拍摄《更深的井》的视频时差点从悬崖边掉下来</a>。</p><p>在与吉米·法伦谈论冰岛的拍摄时，她说：“我们实际上选择了最糟糕的一周。这是狂风警告——我差点被吹下悬崖。我几乎想，‘这个视频将是我的死亡公告。’”</p><p> 《Deeper Well》获得了<i>NME</i>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kacey-musgraves-deeper-well-review-3601211">三星级评价</a>：“除了含糊的暗示之外，这张唱片的大部分内容让人感觉既可爱又悲伤：这些歌曲建立在诚实的本能之上，是对新感受的直接回应。”</p><p>马斯格雷夫斯还宣布将于 2024 年进行世界巡演，巡演地点包括美国、英国和欧洲。巡演将于 4 月 28 日星期日在都柏林 3Olympia 剧院开始，巡演将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madi-diaz">Madi Diaz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/father-john-misty">Father John Misty</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lord-huron-vide-noir-album-review-2297143">Lord Huron</a>和 Nickel Creek 在特定日期提供支持。</p><p>访问此处获取<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fkacey-musgraves-tickets%2Fartist%2F1668663" target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国和欧洲门票</a>，访问此处获取<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fkacey-musgraves-tickets%2Fartist%2F1668663" target="_blank" rel="noopener">美国门票</a>。请<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-recalls-nearly-falling-off-a-cliff-while-filming-new-music-video-3602486">在此处</a>查看完整的巡演日期列表。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kacey-musgraves-perform-she-calls-me-back-with-noah-kahan-3603872">观看凯西·马斯格雷夫斯 (Kacey Musgraves) 与诺亚·卡汉 (Noah Kahan) 表演《她呼唤我回来》(She Calls Me Back) 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
杰克·吉伦哈尔仍然想扮演蝙蝠侠：“这将是一种荣幸” https://www.nme.com/news/film/jake-gyllenhaal-still-wants-to-play-batman-it-would-be-an-honour-3603862?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jake-gyllenhaal-仍然想玩蝙蝠侠，这将是一种荣幸Surej SinghWed, 20 Mar 2024 07:03:29 +0000 Film NewsNewsbatmanDChttps://www.nme.com/?p=3603862 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，吉伦哈尔是克里斯托弗·诺兰三部曲主角的有力竞争者，但最终输给了克里斯蒂安·贝尔</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jake-gyllenhaal-still-wants-to-play-batman-it-would-be-an-honour-3603862">杰克·吉伦哈尔仍然想扮演蝙蝠侠：“这将是一种荣幸”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jake-gyllenhaal">杰克·吉伦哈尔</a>透露，如果有机会，他很想扮演<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/batman">蝙蝠侠</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-batman-review-robert-pattinson-3171137">《蝙蝠侠》评论：与罗伯特·帕丁森的黑暗骑士一起陷入困境</a></strong></li></ul><p>随着<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-gunn">詹姆斯·冈恩</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/dc">DC 宇宙</a>开始成形，超级英雄世界中的更多角色正在被选角，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-corenswet-and-rachel-brosnahan-cast-james-gunns-superman-legacy-3462163">超人</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/house-of-the-dragon-milly-alcock-supergirl-in-james-gunn-dc-universe-3578976">女超人</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/nicholas-hoult-reportedly-cast-as-lex-luthor-in-superman-legacy-3545021">莱克斯·卢瑟</a>。然而，蝙蝠侠/布鲁斯·韦恩是一位尚未确定的英雄。</p><p>杰克·吉伦哈尔（Jake Gyllenhaal）一直是蝙蝠侠角色的常年竞争者，最近有人问他是否有可能在冈恩的 DC 宇宙中饰演斗篷十字军。吉伦哈尔对<a href="https://screenrant.com/jake-gyllenhaal-dcu-batman-role-response/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Screen Rant</em></a>说：“哦，伙计。这是一个经典的[角色]。这是一种荣幸。说到扮演其他令人难以置信的演员过去扮演过的角色……” </p><figure id="attachment_3577085" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3577085" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3577085" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jake-Gyllenhaal-Road-House.jpg" alt="杰克·吉伦哈尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jake-Gyllenhaal-Road-House.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jake-Gyllenhaal-Road-House-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jake-Gyllenhaal-Road-House-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jake-Gyllenhaal-Road-House-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jake-Gyllenhaal-Road-House-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jake-Gyllenhaal-Road-House-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3577085" class="wp-caption-text">杰克·吉伦哈尔于 2022 年 3 月 27 日在加利福尼亚州好莱坞。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Jeff Kravitz/FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p>吉伦哈尔进一步说道：“当我想到这一点时，我将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-washington">丹泽尔·华盛顿</a>一起在<em>《奥赛罗》</em>中扮演伊阿古，我会想到一直以来扮演这个角色的演员的历史，我对此感到害怕。这是第一级。这就是我现在正在做的事情。但是当然。这将永远是一种荣幸。那些类型的事情和那些角色都是经典。”</p><p>自2000年代初以来，吉伦哈尔就与布鲁斯·韦恩/蝙蝠侠联系在一起，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>宣布将把蝙蝠侠改编成银幕，后来被称为<em>“黑暗骑士三部曲”</em> 。据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/03/jake-gyllenhaal-batman-1235862889/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞截止日期》</em></a>报道，吉伦哈尔曾参加过这个角色的试镜，并被认为是最有力的竞争者，但最终输给了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christian-bale">克里斯蒂安·贝尔</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3171336" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3171336" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3171336" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson.jpg" alt="蝙蝠侠" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3171336" class="wp-caption-text">罗伯特·帕丁森首次亮相蝙蝠侠。图片来源：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/jake-gyllenhaal-could-replace-ben-affleck-as-batman-2162086">2017 年，马特·里夫斯开始</a>为<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-batman"><em>《蝙蝠侠》</em></a>寻找演员，吉伦哈尔再次与这位超级英雄联系在一起，最终选择了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-pattinson">罗伯特·帕丁森</a>。</p><p>再次由帕丁森主演、里维斯领衔主演的<em>《蝙蝠侠第二部》</em>最近透露，由于去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/actors-strike-ends-sag-aftra-studios-agree-to-deal-hollywood-reacts-3534652">美国演员工会</a>和美国演员工会和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wga-ends-hollywood-writers-strike-tentative-deal-details-3504715">世界电影协会罢工</a>造成的延误，该片将推迟一整年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-batman-part-2-wont-be-coming-out-anytime-soon-3600561">直到 2026 年 10 月上映</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对<em>《蝙蝠侠》</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-batman-review-robert-pattinson-3171137">四星评论</a>中写道：“导演马特·里夫斯将粗暴的黑帮戏剧与黑色电影侦探惊悚片混合在一起，而且多亏了达诺饰演的超级令人毛骨悚然的反派，还带来了一些心理<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/horror">恐怖</a>。大多数时候，它都会表现得很出色。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jake-gyllenhaal-still-wants-to-play-batman-it-would-be-an-honour-3603862">杰克·吉伦哈尔仍然想扮演蝙蝠侠：“这将是一种荣幸”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
